This dir would be mounted to /my_product/media/bootanimation/
by 'post-fs-data.sh'.

'bootanimation.zip' is startup animation.

'rbootanimation.zip' is the animation for both 'Power off' and 'Restart'.

'poweroff.ogg' will be played when poweroff or restart.
The 'poweroff.ogg' in ColorOS_Mod repository is the music "Quick Metal Riff 1.mp3" written by Brett VanDonsel, which is available for commercial and non-commercial purposes.

